<para style="p">A song of ascents, of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />I was glad when they said to me,</para>

<para style="q1">"Let us go to the house of Yahweh."</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Jerusalem, our feet are standing</para>

<para style="q1">within your gates!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Jerusalem, built</para>

<para style="q1">as a city carefully planned!</para>
